                                                },
                                                "TagText" : {
                                                   "handle" : "h8cd4440egd715g411bga677gf999ae1657f2",
                                                   "type" : 28, "value" : "Don't get me wrong, I like a wee gossip as much as the rest, but Caitlin does get a bit carried away with the tall tales. ",
